# ProTax 1040 App (Next.js + Tailwind)

A ready-to-deploy client portal prototype: secure uploads (demo), appointments (Calendly), login (demo), and dashboard.

## Quick Start (Local)
1) Install Node.js 18+
2) npm install
3) npm run dev
4) Open http://localhost:3000

## Deploy on Vercel
- Import this repo in Vercel (Framework: Next.js)
- Click Deploy

## Domain
- Add `app.protax1040.org` to the Vercel project (Settings ‚Üí Domains)
- At your registrar, create a CNAME for `app` ‚Üí `cname.vercel-dns.com`

## Notes
- Uploads are demo only; replace with your storage (S3 + presigned URLs, etc.).
- Login is demo only; connect to your auth (Clerk/Auth0/Supabase) later.
